    "updated_at": "2016-01-16T14:51:53Z",
    "body": "Setting default font for international language is quite complex and I don't think Chromium has exposed related APIs, so adding API to set default font will unlikely be implemented.\n\nAs for the `font-face` problem, can you try if you can reproduce the same problem in Chrome 47? We need to verify whether it is a bug of Electron or Chromium.\n"
