    "body": "Can you report this to [Chromium's issues list](https://crbug.com)? The problem is inside Chromium so we are not able to fix this on Electron's side.\n\nAlso does changing the default font fix the problem in Chrome? It is possible to add API to change the global default font, e.g. the ones showed in `chrome://settings/fonts`.\n"
